-- Sberbank banks on organic growth in eastern Europe
-- By Michael Shields
-- Thu Jun 12, 2014 04:33AM EDT
-- None



VIENNA, June 12 (Reuters) - Sberbank <SBER.MM>, Russia's largest lender, is focusing on organic growth for its central and eastern European operations, its European chief said on Thursday.

"The next year and a half to two years, the focus will be organic," Mark Arnold told journalists in Vienna.